Instructions:
- Do NOT modify existing Strapi content types or schemas
- Do NOT rename, remove, or repurpose Strapi fields
- Do NOT change existing data-fetching logic or API endpoints
- Do NOT replace Strapi-driven content with static data
- Presentation-level changes must consume existing Strapi data as-is

If SEO or conversion improvements require content changes:
- Adjust presentation or copy only
- Do NOT alter Strapi data structures

If unsure, ask or warn before making changes.
